algorithm_01.transcribed_answer:
int binarySearch (int[] nums, int target) {
    int low=0;
    int high=nums.length;
    while (low<high) {
        int mid=(low+high)
        if (nums[mid]==target) {
            return mid;
        }
        else if (nums[mid]<target) {
            low=mid;
        } else {
            high=mid;
        }
    }
    return -1
}
复杂度 O(log n)

